highlights.text: Henrique & Juliano has the most spots on Top Songs Brazil. “Última Saudade - Ao Vivo” is the highest at #12.
“BATE VOLTA” by DJ TOPO, MC Kevin o Chris, and Luísa Sonza is the highest new entry on Top Songs Brazil at #129.
“Lapada Dela - Ao Vivo” by Grupo Menos É Mais and Matheus Fernandes has been on Top Songs Brazil the longest, at 890 days straight.
“Dono da Sua Cama - Ao Vivo” by Bruno & Denner and Luan Pereira is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Brazil, up 92 spots at #85.
